To create a new distribution:

- Update version in setup.py
- Install and run tests to check if things work as expected
- Update top-level README
- Run 'python setup.py sdist'
- git 
  - commit,
  - tag e.g.  git tag -a v0.31 -m 'my version 0.31')
  -  push and push origin --tags
- Upload source and update sourceforge website
